## Project Principles

- Build in small, working phases.
- Prefer clear and explainable code over clever abstractions.
- Keep services containerized.
- Avoid committing secrets.
- Treat local AI as infrastructure, not as a paid external dependency.
- Make the project useful for learning, portfolio review, and eventual personal use.

